Automation and Programmability Benefits

- Can be used for:
    - Device Configuration
    - Initial device provisioning
    - Software version control
    - Collecting statistics from devices
    - Compliance verification
    - Reports
    - Troubleshooting
    
- Network programmability enables automation, reducing human to machine interaction
- Recuces likelihood of human error
- More salable than configuring one device at a time
- Provides configuration and software version control

# Automation Methods

  - There are multiple ways to implement network automation
      1. Python scripts
      2.NETCONF
      3. RESTCONF
      4. Ansible
      5. Puppet
      6. Chef
      7. SDN
      8. Cisco DNA Center
      and more
      
  - Not all methods are supported by all devices

